            "value" : "GluVib displays most data as soon as it becomes available in Apple Health. This applies to metrics such as Nutrition entries, Activity and movement data, workouts, and insulin records. Continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) (Sensor) data is an exception (see next)."
          }
        }
